# Testing the Detection System

To test Snort detection, a ping request was sent from another terminal or machine.

```bash
ping 192.168.1.5
```

Snort detected the ICMP traffic and generated alerts similar to the following:

```
[**] [1:1000001:1] Ping Detected [**]
```

